def_cn: 世界领袖(尤指经济强国的国家领导人)
def_en: A world leader is someone who is the leader of a country, especially an economically powerful country.

def_cn: (某一领域中的)尖端产品，世界领先者，领头羊
def_en: A product, company, organization, or person that is a world leader is the most successful or advanced one in a particular area of activity.
